The Rocketmobile

Every good Team Rocket needs a ridiculous vehicle.

Pantheon’s version would be The Money Bin.

Not a vault of gold.

A vault of:

* Patterns.
* Tools.
* Stories.
* Relationships.
* Lessons.
* Seeds.

The more people contribute, the larger it becomes.

The treasure isn’t stored wealth.

The treasure is reusable capability.

